text.tspan: This is one piece of a Split Bitcoin Key. It is given to the above named trustee to keep safe
(protected from damage) and secure (it should only be accessible to the trustee).
- be returned only to the owner upon their request.
- be given to the designated executor of the will of the owner, if they have perished.
- never be given to (or even accessed by) any other person.
Please contact the owner if this SBK Piece is damaged or if there is a chance that somebody
other than the trustee had access it.
